      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FORGERY (1) was unwanted in betting but burnt to an early lead and scored an all the way win over 530m at this track in Other, scoring by 6 lengths (30.54). Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks the testing material. GIGGLE MONSTER (8) is a talented type who pinged the lids and cleared the pack early, leading throughout to a dominant win (30.67) at this track in Maiden over 530m. Brilliant beginner who should be leading the way here. Leading chance again. TOBY KEEPING (4) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (30.79) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to feature in the finish. WEBLEC PEBBLES (6) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot in a fast run most recently.",
